data.description: Calling all buyers looking for an amazing home!  Here's one worth taking a look;  it is a townhouse with stunning features situated in the Village of Northwoods. Located across from an A-rated school, New Berlin Elementary,  3 bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms over 1400 square feet is a two-story beauty with a one car garage and a screened lanai.    The home consists of granite countertops in the kitchen with a bar separating the living area. Downstairs is fully tiled with an half bathroom and upstairs have carpet in bedrooms.  The owner's suite has dual closets and located upstairs on the backside of the townhouse.  All appliances stay including the new washer and dryer.
